* GFC：通用流量控制
* VPI：虚拟路径标识符
* VCI：虚拟频道标识符
* PT：有效载荷类型
* CLP：拥塞丢失优先级
* HEC：错误控制

==部署与应用==
ATM在20世纪90年代初受到电信公司和部分计算机制造商的青睐。然而，即使到了90年代末，基于互联网协议的产品仍比ATM有更好的性价比。<ref name="bellheads">{{Cite news |title= Netheads vs Bellheads |author= Steve Steinberg |work= Wired |date= October 1996 |volume= 4 |number= 10 |url= https://www.wired.com/wired/archive/4.10/atm.html |accessdate= 24 September 2011 |archive-date= 2014-03-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140301100805/http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/4.10/atm.html }}</ref>
[[FORE_Systems|FORE Systems]]等公司专注于ATM产品<ref>{{Cite news |title= What's in store for FORE? |page= 12 |work= Network World |date= 16 September 1996 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=IxgEAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA12 |accessdate=24 September 2011 }}</ref>，而其他大型厂商，如[[思科|思科]]等，则仅将ATM视作一种额外的选择。

